"its no replacement for manual testing"



  __________APPLICATION__________
  |                             |
  |    UNIT             UNIT    |
  |                             |
  |    UNIT             UNIT    |
  
  
  UNIT: e.g., a function, class, a component
  
  
  -> we test all the single units -> if all units are working -> the app is working
  
